data.description: INVESTOR'S DREAM... Introducing an enticing investment opportunity - a home with immense potential that's sure to catch the eye of savvy investors. This home presents an exciting prospect for investors seeking a diamond in the rough. Its 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, and partially finished basement, along with the screened back porch, fenced backyard, and generous storage options, paint a picture of potential waiting to be unlocked. With a touch of creativity and the right vision, this property could be transformed into a highly sought-after gem in the real estate market. NO HOA or RENTAL RESTRICTIONS!!
